Feature: Product Search Functionality

  Scenario: Enter  search term and verify  results
    Given I open the browser and enter the URL 
     
   When I enter a valid product name as <productName> in the search bar
    And I click on the search button
    Then I should see search results for <expectedProductName>
Examples:
| productName|                                  |expectedProductName|
 |"sofa"|                                       |" sofa"|
 |""|                                            |"Search our store"|
 |"perfumes"|                                    |"perfumes"|
 |"sufo"|                                         |"No results found"|
 |"Industrial Tan 90cm Studded Back Bench"|       |" Industrial Tan 90cm Studded Back Bench"|

